        "endTime": 12.185,
        "duration": 3.419,
        "sentenceIndex": 97
      },
      {
        "text": "Emma started a campaign to collect and give one thousand books.",
        "startTime": 12.185,
        "endTime": 16.768,
        "duration": 4.583,
        "sentenceIndex": 98
      },
      {
        "text": "She named it the Thousand Books campaign.",
