        "endTime": 11.299,
        "duration": 3.843,
        "sentenceIndex": 102
      },
      {
        "text": "Emma wrote a book to help kids be activists.",
        "startTime": 11.299,
        "endTime": 14.366,
        "duration": 3.066,
        "sentenceIndex": 103
      },
      {
        "text": "The hardest part of the campaign was learning about entitlement.",
